.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-SET-LABEL" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-set-label \- set a display label for a wallet
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-set-label
.I wallet_name label
.SH DESCRIPTION
Stores a display label in the wallet's metadata table.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"status":"updated","wallet":"<name>","label":"<label>"}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-info (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-tag (1)
